marketing: Shell Corena S3 R is a premium quality air compressor oil designed to deliver high performance lubrication of rotary sliding vane and screw air compressors. Formulated with severely hydrogenated base fluids in combination with an advanced additive system provides excellent protection and performance for compressors with oil maintenance intervals up to 4,000 hours (where allowed by manufacturers).
